## Examples  
 L'esempio seguente cerca un determinato <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> e consente di visualizzare il <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Name%2A> e <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Parent%2A> del risultato.  
  
```vb  
Dim myADSPath As String = _   
          "LDAP://onecity/CN=user,CN=Users,DC=onecity,DC=corp,DC=fabrikam,DC=com"  
Dim myDirectoryEntry As New DirectoryEntry(myADSPath, UserName, SecurelyStoredPassword)  
  
Console.WriteLine("Parent is :" + myDirectoryEntry.Parent.Path)  
  
```  
  
```csharp  
String myADSPath = "LDAP://onecity/CN=user,CN=Users,DC=onecity,DC=corp,DC=fabrikam,DC=com";  
DirectoryEntry myDirectoryEntry=new DirectoryEntry(myADSPath, UserName, SecurelyStoredPassword);  
  
Console.WriteLine("Parent is :"+myDirectoryEntry.Parent.Path);  
```  
  
```cpp#  
String^ myADSPath = "LDAP://onecity/CN=user,CN=Users,DC=onecity,DC=corp,DC=fabrikam,DC=com";  
DirectoryEntry^ myDirectoryEntry = gcnew DirectoryEntry(myADSPath, UserName, SecurelyStoredPassword);  
  
Console::WriteLine("Parent is :{0}", myDirectoryEntry->Parent->Path);  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 È possibile impostare il <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> e <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> proprietà per specificare credenziali alternative con cui accedere alle informazioni in servizi di dominio Active Directory. Qualsiasi altra <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> gli oggetti recuperati da questa istanza (ad esempio tramite <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>) vengono create automaticamente con le stesse credenziali alternative.  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrato il <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> e <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> delle proprietà del <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> classe. Questo esempio mostra come ottenere specificata dall'utente <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> e il <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> di tutti i relativi <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>.  
  
```vb  
Dim myADSPath As String = _  
      "LDAP://onecity/CN=Users,DC=onecity,DC=corp,DC=fabrikam,DC=com"  
  
' Create an Instance of DirectoryEntry.  
Dim myDirectoryEntry As New DirectoryEntry(myADSPath)  
myDirectoryEntry.Username = UserName  
myDirectoryEntry.Password = SecurelyStoredPassword  
  
' Get the Child ADS objects.  
Console.WriteLine("The Child ADS objects are:")  
Dim myChildDirectoryEntry As DirectoryEntry  
For Each myChildDirectoryEntry In  myDirectoryEntry.Children  
   Console.WriteLine(myChildDirectoryEntry.Path)  
Next myChildDirectoryEntry   
```  
  
```csharp  
